# Patidar Cricket League (PCL) Website

## Overview
This is the official website for the Patidar Cricket League tournament, featuring live match updates, team management, points tables, and fixture scheduling.

## Features
- 🎬 **Live Match Updates** - Real-time commentary and scoreboard
- 📊 **Points Table** - Live standings and team statistics
- 🗓️ **Fixtures & Results** - Complete match schedule
- 👥 **Team Management** - Team profiles and player information
- 📱 **Responsive Design** - Works on all devices
- 🔒 **Admin Panel** - Secure tournament management

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React 18, Tailwind CSS
- **Database**: Firebase Firestore
- **Server**: Node.js (built-in, no npm required)
- **Hosting**: Ready for deployment

## Quick Start
```bash
node server.js
# Visit http://localhost:3000
```

